title: Contact
body:
We'd love to hear from you! Feel free to reach out to us using the following information:

  • Address: 123 Civic Plaza, Suite 456, New York, NY 10001
  • Email: support@example.com
  • Phone: (212) 123-4567

Our office hours are Monday through Friday, 9:00 AM to 5:00 PM Eastern Time.

Please note that due to high call volumes, you may experience longer than usual wait times. For faster service, we recommend using our digital tools or contacting us via email.
